Class PredicateRowFilterAssembler

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assembler, HBaseFilterAssembler, PredicateFilterAssembler, org.plasma.query.visitor.QueryVisitor

    public class PredicateRowFilterAssembler
extends RowPredicateVisitor
implements PredicateFilterAssembler
    Processes a where predicate expression tree into a set of HBase row filters arranged within a hierarchy of HBase filter lists. The resulting filter list resembles the given expression tree with AND/OR MUST_PASS_ALL/MUST_PASS_ONE semantics representing the input. A filter list stack is maintained which mirrors the query expression being processed.
    Since:
    0.5
    Author:
    Scott Cinnamond
